                            ],
                            Label: "goodbye_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Two of us in the pit at once, and you still walked out standing. Take the last of the floor to Bruno - and tell him the iron rang for you."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "His team is older and heavier than ours. Bring something that does not mind taking a hit. Free advice, the best kind."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Ken - the pit remembers",
                    Label: "beaten"
                },
                {
                    Conditions: [
                        {
