                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Half the floor came through here sore and grumbling about you. My best partners drilled with them this morning - you caught me on a slow day. Striker lent nobody anything, though. He is fresh, and he is standing right beside me."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The pit rule does not bend - Striker and I fight as one side, and Rocky of the sparring floor takes your corner. Say the word."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Ken - the pit, two on two",
                    Label: "ready_weakened"
                },
