                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Found the pit, did you. Bruno does not keep his apprentices standing in a lobby - we train where the pit is deep and the iron is loud. Apprentice Ken, and beside me Jr. Apprentice Striker. Down here the rule is one bout, both of us across from you at once."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The gym lends every challenger a second - Rocky of the sparring floor stands your corner. The masters on the floor are optional: each one you put down leaves my side of the pit a little more tired, or you take us at full strength right now. The choice is the lesson. Say the word."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Ken - the pit, two on two",
                    Label: "ready"
                }
